head, Siobhan and Kay, Michael and Brown, Jacqueline and Murnane, Clare and Gray, Emma and Humphries, Matthew and Sycamore, Neil and Barker, Darren and Saunders, David and Wallis, Justene and Babbage, Anne and Hammond, Sian and Mashreghi-Mohammadi, Maryam and Barr, Lucy and Martin, Sancha and Wray, Paul and Ellington, Andrew and Matthews, Nicholas and Ellwood, Matthew and Woodmansey, Rebecca and Clark, Graham and Cooper, James D and Cooper, James and Tromans, Anthony and Grafham, Darren and Skuce, Carl and Pandian, Richard and Andrews, Robert and Harrison, Elliot and Kimberley, Andrew and Garnett, Jane and Fosker, Nigel and Hall, Rebekah and Garner, Patrick and Kelly, Daniel and Bird, Christine and Palmer, Sophie and Gehring, Ines and Berger, Andrea and Dooley, Christopher M and Ersan-Ürün, Zübeyde and Eser, Cigdem and Geiger, Horst and Geisler, Maria and Karotki, Lena and Kirn, Anette and Konantz, Judith and Konantz, Martina and Oberländer, Martina and Rudolph-Geiger, Silke and Teucke, Mathias and Lanz, Christa and Raddatz, Günter and Osoegawa, Kazutoyo and Zhu, Baoli and Rapp, Amanda and Widaa, Sara and Langford, Cordelia and Yang, Fengtang and Schuster, Stephan C and Carter, Nigel P and Harrow, Jennifer and Ning, Zemin and Herrero, Javier and Searle, Steve M J and Enright, Anton and Geisler, Robert and Plasterk, Ronald H A and Lee, Charles and Westerfield, Monte and de Jong, Pieter J and Zon, Leonard I and Postlethwait, John H and Nüsslein-Volhard, Christiane and Hubbard, Tim J P and Roest Crollius, Hugues and Rogers, Jane and Stemple, Derek L},
pages = {498-503},
